<h2>@ViewBag.Title.</h2>

<p>FolloThru is a collaborative contract management tool designed to add value to both parties of an agreement by providing transparency, real-time updates, and security. FollowThru utilizes cloud computing to allow its users to access their documents and provide updates on the status of agreements anywhere.</p>

<p>Our software allows users to store contracts, document relevant communication of the concerned parties, and track and notify parties of contract milestones. Our goal is to provide complete transparency over the life cycle of a contract to all parties involved, as well as eliminate the need for physical paper contracts and e-mail attachment contracts. </p>

